### Register Donor
POST http://localhost:12000/auth/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alex",
  "lastName": "Patel",
  "email": "donor1@mail.com",
  "role": "DONOR",
  "password": "donor123"
}

### Login Donor
POST http://localhost:12000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "donor1@mail.com", "password": "donor123" }

### View Cases Needing Support
GET http://localhost:12000/donor-api/cases
Authorization: Bearer 6a080e341eb66ab002de721c

### Pledge to a Case
POST http://localhost:12000/donor-api/pledge/6a0805503f1df1a92b5eaee0
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer 6a080e341eb66ab002de721c

{ "amount": 50, "message": "For vet checkup" }

### View My Pledges
GET http://localhost:12000/donor-api/my-pledges
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_DONOR_TOKEN